Stox 2.7 project

Source: R/ProjectIO.R
stox27project.Rd

Nested list representation of Stox 2.7 projects.

Details

Naming and definitions follow the XML. Stox 2.7 projects conforms roughly to the namespace http://www.imr.no/formats/stox/v1.2, defined at http://www.imr.no/formats/stox/v1.2/stoxv1_2.xsd and in formats/stoxv2.7.xsd.

This schema is used with some additions in the representation, with the data type mapping:

xs:string

character

xs:boolean

logical

In addition to structures defined in this schema, stox 2.7 may store the following structures:

platformfactor

list of lists with members 'value', 'covariatesourcetype', 'covariate'.

covparam

list of lists with members 'value', 'covariatetable', 'parameter'
